      female: 'She drank the Tegal because refusing was a statement she was not ready to make. The world expanded and contracted in a way that she had not experienced before and has not been able to fully describe since. The augur said something during the expansion that she cannot now remember except as a feeling. The feeling had a direction to it. She is still moving in that direction and has not yet decided whether this was a choice.',
