      female: 'She accompanied the border trader to the post. The Kaldorics looked at her with the kind of careful not-looking that meant they had noticed her and decided not to acknowledge it. She looked back with the kind of careful not-looking that meant she was watching everything. The market was smaller than she had imagined and contained things she had not seen before. She noted which things and what they were worth.',
