      male:   'The contract was for three years, renewable at mutual pleasure. The noble\'s steward set the terms and they were generous — room, board, a guaranteed wage at the bonded rate, and access to materials he could not have afforded himself. He had not held a franchise and did not miss it. The work was harder here, the expectations higher, and the silence of the private workshop was worth the constraint.',
      female: 'She had been offered the bonded contract by a lord\'s factor who had heard of her skill. It meant giving up her journeyman freedom, but the workshop he described — fitted to her specifications, supplied without bargaining — was not something she could have built herself. She signed for five years and extended twice.',
