      female: 'She had been examined by three syndics, one of whom was clearly hoping she would fail. She did not fail. She answered every question exactly, produced the requested demonstration piece, and thanked each of them individually afterward. The one who had been hoping she would fail did not meet her eyes. She found she did not mind this.',
