      female: 'She watched the masked figure and the Kaldoric merchant negotiate in a language she had not been taught. The augur\'s posture was relaxed. The merchant\'s was not. Afterwards the augur said the trade was fair. She noted that fair was a Hârnic concept and wondered if the Kaldoric word meant the same thing as the Pagaelin one.',
